Place the plate on the shelf with the shaker, to the left of the shaker.

high_descs: Go forward, and then left to go around to the island.
Pick up the plate from the center of the island.
Hold the plate and turn around to the fridge on the right side.

Place the plate on the next to bottom shelf.
